data.description: Discover the perfect investment opportunity close to Miami International Airport! Duplex functioning as a non-conforming triplex. This spacious duplex for sale offers income potential, making it an ideal addition to your portfolio. These two remodeled units have new AC units, remodeled kitchens and baths. Plenty of parking and a concrete driveway. It promises both comfortable living and excellent rental prospects. Contact us today for a private viewing and secure your investment in the thriving real estate market.
